// Semantic direction:
// p2p_nettverk enables decentralized communication between node_p2p instances.
// multiadresse encodes multiple transport layers in one string (e.g. /ip4/1.2.3.4/tcp/4001).
// hole_punching coordinates simultaneous connection attempts through NAT from both sides.
// kademlia_dht is the distributed hash table where xor_avstand defines node proximity.
// k_bøtte stores the k closest known nodes for each distance bit-prefix.
// dht_finn_node iteratively queries closer and closer nodes toward a target node_id.
// cid (Content IDentifier) is a self-describing hash that addresses content by its multihash.
// ipfs_legg_til hashes data to a CID and distributes it to the nearest dht noder.
// rykteprotokoll spreads messages by each node forwarding to fanout_gossip random peers.
// gossip_historikk deduplicates messages so nodes ignore already-seen gossip_id values.
// gossipsub builds a stable mesh_peer set per topic and uses score_peer to drop bad peers.
// grafting adds a peer to the mesh when coverage is low; pruning_p2p removes excess peers.
// yamux and mplex are stream multiplexing protocols that run many logical strøm_p2p over one connection.
// multistream_select negotiates which protokoll to use at connection setup.
// tilkoblings_leder enforces peer_limit and evicts low-scoring peers when capacity is reached.

// Primitive flow:
// node start: p2p_start -> last node_id(privat_nøkkel) -> bind transport_tcp + quic
//   oppdagelse: mdns broadcast -> finn lokale noder | bootstrap_noder -> koble til
//   kademlia: dht_finn_node(node_id) -> fyll k_bøtter med nære noder
// dht_put(nøkkel, verdi): beregn xor_avstand(nøkkel, alle kjente noder)
//   send PUT til k nærmeste noder -> de lagrer og republiserer
// dht_get(nøkkel): finn k nærmeste til nøkkel -> spør om verdi
//   returnerer første treff | samler svar fra kvorum
// gossipsub: publiser_p2p(emne, melding) -> send til mesh_peer sett (D=6)
//   mottaker: sjekk gossip_historikk -> ny? videresend til egne mesh-peers
// ipfs_hent(cid): dht_finn_verdi(cid) -> finn tilbydere -> koble -> strøm_p2p blokk

// This defines P2P networking: Kademlia DHT, content addressing with CIDs, epidemic gossip,
// GossipSub mesh pub/sub, stream multiplexing, NAT traversal, and peer scoring.
